You know it, they know it: school sucks. Express your frustration with being forced to sit in a plastic chair and memorize pointless facts for eight hours a day with the all-new School Sucks Pack.

Includes 30 new Family Edition cards like &ldquo;Paying Dad five dollars to do my homework&rdquo; and &ldquo;Being unable to learn, because I am a pine cone.&rdquo;

&mdash;description from the publisher

Are you frightened by your child&rsquo;s formidable intellect? Then your family will love the all-new Smarty Pants Pack.

Features 30 deliciously cerebral new Family Edition cards like &ldquo;Calculating the volume of a sphere,&rdquo; &ldquo;Getting my butt stuck in a black hole,&rdquo; and &ldquo;An authentic 250-year-old George Washington turd.&rdquo;

&mdash;description from the publisher

Destination Dash is a print & play single-player card game where you assume the role of a pilot from a private jet company responsible for ferrying affluent clients worldwide. Your objective is to successfully transport the appropriate number of passengers to all 8 destinations before exhausting your available aircraft.

